<li><span class="citation book">Smith, Paul Allan (1995). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://books.google.com.au/books?id=xeVIBodlZLgC&printsec=frontcover&dq=Trito-Isaiah#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false"><i>Rhetoric and redaction in Trito-Isaiah: the structure, growth, and authorship of Isaiah 56–66</i></a>. Leiden and New York: Brill. <a href="International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="Special_BookSources/90-04-10306-6" title="Special:BookSources/90-04-10306-6">90-04-10306-6</a><span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://books.google.com.au/books?id=xeVIBodlZLgC&printsec=frontcover&dq=Trito-Isaiah#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false">http://books.google.com.au/books?id=xeVIBodlZLgC&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;dq=Trito-Isaiah#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false</a></span>.</span></li>
